# 7. 清理旧引用块
python "Auxiliary script/strip_legacy_blocks.py"

# 8. 修复 backup 原本的死链
python "Auxiliary script/fix_dead_links_v2.py"

# 9. 验证
python "Auxiliary script/validation_script.py"
python "Auxiliary script/governance_script.py"
```

## A.3 单文档修复

```python
# 编辑 frontmatter 字段
from pathlib import Path
fp = Path('memory/api/networking.md')
content = fp.read_text(encoding='utf-8')
# ... 修改 ...
fp.write_text(new_content, encoding='utf-8')
```

## A.4 长期维护脚本三件套 ⭐ V3.1 新增

```bash
cd "C:\CherryStudio\Agent\UdonSharpAgent"

# 1. 知识库与备份的纯粹知识差异(剔除 frontmatter 噪声)
python "Auxiliary script/pure_knowledge_audit.py"

# 2. 外链健康检查(16 线程并发,检测 references 中的 URL 失效)
python "Auxiliary script/url_health_check.py"

# 3. GitHub Releases 版本号批量核对(VRChat SDK / VPM 包)
python "Auxiliary script/version_audit_script.py"
```

**运行频率建议**:
- `pure_knowledge_audit.py`: 每次大入库后 + 灾难恢复 step 0
- `url_health_check.py`: 每月一次
- `version_audit_script.py`: VRChat SDK / 主要 VPM 包发布后

